c0fed6dd-e590-411c-a97d-ded39bc635be	talking-during-sex-activity	How do you feel about talking during sex?	sexual-activities	13	{"options": ["Want us to talk openly about what feels good", "Some talking sounds good but I might be naturally quieter", "More comfortable with non-verbal communication", "Prefer to focus on the physical connection without much talking"]}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	13	t	Some people are naturally more vocal during sex, others are quieter. Both are normal.	1.00	\N	t	multiple_choice	\N
c1516128-2112-4c5b-bf11-fd5376ae84a9	knowledge-level	How much do you actually know about what happens during sex?	sexual-knowledge	2	{"options": ["I feel pretty well-informed about the physical and emotional realities", "I understand the basics but know there is more to learn", "I have a general idea but lots of questions about what it is really like", "I really do not know much about the actual experience"]}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-25 16:18:58.07801+00	2	t	There is no shame in not knowing much - most people saving sex for marriage learn from bits and pieces.	1.00	\N	t	multiple_choice	What would help you both feel more prepared and confident about your sexual relationship together?
1447d9c2-f298-4826-abfa-cd075ef669cd	pain-expectations	What are your expectations about pain during first-time sex?	sexual-knowledge	3	{"options": ["I have heard it is really painful and I am pretty worried about it", "I expect some discomfort at first but think it will get better quickly", "I do not really expect pain - maybe just some newness to adjust to", "I honestly have no idea what to expect and that makes me nervous"]}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-25 16:18:58.07801+00	3	t	You have probably heard different stories about first-time sex - some scary, some not.	1.00	\N	t	multiple_choice	How can you support each other through any physical adjustments in your early intimate experiences?
27ee9792-70b7-48b4-9bd3-d41e61f91176	orgasm-knowledge	Rate your knowledge about orgasms and sexual climax:	sexual-knowledge	4	{"max": 5, "min": 1, "labels": {"1": "I really do not know anything about this", "2": "I have heard the word but do not know much", "3": "I have a basic idea but lots of questions", "4": "I understand the basics pretty well", "5": "I feel well-informed about this topic"}}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-25 16:18:58.07801+00	4	t	Orgasms are a normal part of sexual pleasure, but many people do not really understand what they are or how they work.	1.00	\N	t	scale	What would make you both feel comfortable learning about sexual pleasure together?
a6a98178-a7b8-44e2-84c8-5aff03e414e5	female-arousal	What do you know about how women get aroused and what they need to feel pleasure?	sexual-knowledge	5	{"options": ["I understand pretty well how this works", "I know some basics but there is more to learn", "I know very little about this", "I have never really learned about this topic"]}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-25 16:18:58.07801+00	5	t	Understanding how womens bodies respond sexually is crucial for a satisfying marriage, regardless of your gender.	1.00	\N	t	multiple_choice	How do you want to approach learning about what brings each other pleasure?
4e777401-bfa7-4b7d-9f5c-ad05b7427d60	male-arousal	What do you know about how men get aroused and what they need to feel satisfied?	sexual-knowledge	6	{"options": ["I understand pretty well how this works", "I know some basics but there is more to learn", "I know very little about this", "I have never really learned about this topic"]}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-25 16:18:58.07801+00	6	t	Male sexuality might seem straightforward, but there is more to learn about what men actually need for satisfying intimacy.	1.00	\N	t	multiple_choice	What would help you both communicate openly about your physical needs and responses?
9fda89fe-8839-4844-b1c9-ed3f38f7abca	nudity-comfort	How do you feel about being completely naked during sex?	sexual-activities	7	{"options": ["Excited/very interested", "Interested but nervous/want to learn", "Neutral/willing to try", "Does not appeal to me/want to say no"]}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-25 16:18:58.07801+00	7	t	Being naked together is the foundation of sexual intimacy. It is normal to feel nervous about this level of vulnerability.	1.00	\N	t	multiple_choice	How can you help each other feel comfortable and confident with physical vulnerability?
f1f7e03a-f30f-44e2-bba0-cfca63ad021f	intercourse	How do you feel about having intercourse (penis in vagina)?	sexual-activities	8	{"options": ["Excited/very interested", "Interested but nervous/want to learn", "Neutral/willing to try", "Does not appeal to me/want to say no"]}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-25 16:18:58.07801+00	8	t	This is probably what you think of most when you imagine sex. Your feelings about it are all completely normal.	1.00	\N	t	multiple_choice	What would help you both approach your first sexual experiences with patience and care?
975cae0f-a54a-4e44-92a1-29bb12385624	manual-stimulation	How do you feel about using your hands to sexually pleasure your partner?	sexual-activities	9	{"options": ["Excited/very interested", "Interested but nervous/want to learn", "Neutral/willing to try", "Does not appeal to me/want to say no"]}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-25 16:18:58.07801+00	9	t	Using your hands to pleasure your partner is often how couples learn what feels good together.	1.00	\N	t	multiple_choice	How do you want to explore physical touch and what feels good for each other?
31089058-392c-4c42-9795-07ee6a062d3c	oral-sex	How do you feel about oral sex in marriage?	sexual-activities	10	{"options": ["Excited/very interested", "Interested but nervous/want to learn", "Neutral/willing to try", "Does not appeal to me/want to say no", "I have concerns about whether this fits our values"]}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-25 16:18:58.07801+00	10	t	This is one of those topics that Christians have different opinions about.	1.00	\N	t	multiple_choice	What values and boundaries do you both want to establish around different expressions of intimacy?
ab31ac39-6bf4-4c8e-9414-e06e713980a0	sexual-experience-virginity	Are you a virgin, and have you and your partner discussed what virginity means to each of you?	sexual-knowledge	1	{"options": ["Yes, I am a virgin and my partner knows this", "No, I am not a virgin but my partner thinks I am a virgin", "No, I am not a virgin and my partner knows this", "We have not discussed our sexual experience levels"]}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-25 16:18:58.07801+00	1	t	People define virginity differently - some count only intercourse, others include oral sex or other intimate activities.	1.00	\N	t	multiple_choice	How can you both feel safe and comfortable discussing your sexual histories and what they mean to each of you?
69ea1a83-bee3-4f57-bbe3-409225b13632	anal-sex	How do you feel about anal sex in marriage?	sexual-activities	11	{"options": ["Interested in trying this", "Curious but want to learn about it safely first", "This does not appeal to me and I want to be able to say no", "I have concerns about whether this fits our values"]}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-25 16:18:58.07801+00	11	t	This is definitely not something all couples try, and it is completely fine to say no.	1.00	\N	t	multiple_choice	How will you communicate about activities that one of you is curious about but the other isn't interested in?
862f631f-62ec-4738-a0c8-76c399c05330	sexual-positions	How do you feel about having sex in different positions?	sexual-activities	12	{"options": ["Very interested in exploring different positions", "Like to try some when we are ready", "Prefer to get comfortable with basics first", "Like the idea of keeping things simple"]}	2025-08-10 17:39:03.892807+00	2025-08-25 16:18:58.07801+00	12	t	There are many ways to have sex beyond the basic position. Some couples love exploring variety, others prefer keeping things simple.	1.00	\N	t	multiple_choice	What approach to exploring intimacy would make you both feel adventurous yet comfortable?
